Package Car

Interface Car

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCar, LargeCar, SmallCar

    public interface Car

    Car.Car Interface

    This is an interface class for objects of Car.Car which features methods that all sub-classes of car must utilise. This class also features a getInstance() factory method for generating instances of car.
